r who rose from nothing and earned power through influence and fear.,Commands BBG operations throughout the city.\r\n0,BBG,Saline Brooks,29,Recruiter,African American,Charismatic and persuasive. Saline is responsible for bringing fresh talent into the organization.,Introduces new gang members and side missions.\r\n0,BBG,Tyrone Bell,35,Enforcer,African American,A feared fighter with a reputation for solving disputes quickly and permanently.,Provides muscle during combat-oriented missions.\r\n0,BBG,Darnell Price,24,Runner,African American,Young ambitious and fearless. Darnell handles deliveries and information exchanges.,Delivers intel and unlocks courier missions.\r\n0,RAVEN,Viktor Volkov,48,Boss,Eastern European,A former military officer turned crime lord. Viktor values order and loyalty and efficiency above all else.,Oversees Raven's international operations.\r\n0,RAVEN,Katya Morozova,33,Assassin,Eastern European,Silent precise and nearly impossible to track. Katya's name alone intimidates enemies.,Supports stealth and elimination missions.\r\n0,RAVEN,Sergei Petrov,38,Arms Dealer,Eastern European,The primary supplier of weapons for Raven. Sergei profits from every conflict in the city.,Unlocks equipment and weapon upgrades.\r\n0,RAVEN,Ivan Kozlov,28,Smuggler,Eastern European,An expert at moving valuable cargo through checkpoints unnoticed.,Opens smuggling and transport missions.\r\n0,SKULLS,Hector Ramirez,44,Boss,Hispanic,A veteran gang leader who rules through respect earned on the streets.,Directs Skulls territory and operations.\r\n0,SKULLS,Diego Cruz,30,Street Captain,Hispanic,Responsible for keeping order in Skulls-controlled neighborhoods.,Guides players through turf-related missions.\r\n0,SKULLS,Elena Torres,26,Scout,Hispanic,Quick observant and always one step ahead. Elena gathers intelligence from across the city.,Reveals enemy activities and hidden objectives.\r\n0,SKULLS,Raul Mendoza,36,Enforcer,Hispanic,A tough veteran who believes actions speak louder than words.,Strengthens combat missions and protection tasks.\r\n0,VULTURES,Freddy Froth,39,Boss,Caucasian,A clever opportunist who profits from chaos and instability wherever it appears.,Leads Vultures and controls black-market activities.\r\n0,VULTURES,Simon O'Sullivan,34,Mechanic,Irish,A talented mechanic capable of rebuilding almost any vehicle from scrap.,Improves vehicles and unlocks performance upgrades.\r\n0,VULTURES,Liam Cooper,29,Smuggler,Caucasian,Specializes in moving rare goods across city borders without attracting attention.,Opens smuggling routes and cargo missions.\r\n0,VULTURES,Connor Blake,32,Collector,Caucasian,Handles debts and payments for the gang. Few people ignore Connor's requests twice.,Collects resources and unlocks finance-related missions.\r\n"]],0,0,[],[],[]],[[{"name":"button","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":500,"height":113},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":500,"height":113},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-250,-56.5,0,250,-56.5,0,-250,56.5,0,250,56.5,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,113,500,113,0,0,500,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-250,"y":-56.5,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":250,"y":56.5,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[5],0,[0],[5],[8]],[[{"name":"icon gallery","rect":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":50,"height":44},"offset":{"x":0,"y":0},"originalSize":{"width":50,"height":44},"rotated":false,"capInsets":[0,0,0,0],"vertices":{"rawPosition":[-25,-22,0,25,-22,0,-25,22,0,25,22,0],"indexes":[0,1,2,2,1,3],"uv":[0,44,50,44,0,0,50,0],"nuv":[0,0,1,0,0,1,1,1],"minPos":{"x":-25,"y":-22,"z":0},"maxPos":{"x":25,"y":22,"z":0}},"packable":true,"pixelsToUnit":100,"pivot":{"x":0.5,"y":0.5},"meshType":0}],[5],0,[0],[5],[9]],[[[46,"Gallery"],[47,"Gallery",33554432,[-26,-27,-28,-29],[[2,-11,[0,"d0iLmnEcJAzJGVM7E4+rWV"],[5,1728,643.894]],[56,45,99.9,100,1,-12,[0,"234q/NhdVK85g9xgofIPyM"]],[64,15,-25,[0,"6bKbpebMNKFoGpuApCJqoc"],-24,-23,-22,-21,-20,-19,-18,-17,-16,